---
layout: base.njk
permalink: index.html
title: "Jingxiao Cai's Blog | Distributed ML Runtime Systems, Agent Ops, Self-Hosted AI"
description: "Technical blog by Jingxiao Cai about distributed ML runtime systems, backend execution reliability, self-hosted AI agents, debugging, automation, and production engineering."
canonicalPath: ""
---
<section class="hero" aria-labelledby="site-title">
  <p class="eyebrow">distributed ML runtime systems · agent ops · self-hosted AI</p>
  <h1 id="site-title">Jingxiao Cai's Blog</h1>
  <p class="hero__lede">Engineering notes on backend/runtime systems for production ML workloads, agent ops, debugging, automation, and the sharp edges of self-hosted AI systems.</p>
  <div class="hero__actions" data-pagefind-ignore>
    <a class="button button--primary" href="{{ site.basePath }}search.html">Search the archive</a>
    <a class="button" href="{{ site.basePath }}feed.xml">RSS feed</a>
    <a class="button" href="{{ site.basePath }}llms.txt">Agent-readable index</a>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="agent-note" aria-labelledby="agent-note-title">
  <h2 id="agent-note-title">Agent-friendly by design</h2>
  <p>Static HTML, stable <code>*.html</code> URLs, RSS, sitemap, Pagefind search, and a generated <code>llms.txt</code> index. No client-rendered content is required for crawlers or AI agents to read the posts.</p>
</section>

<section class="post-list" aria-labelledby="posts-title">
  <div class="section-heading">
    <p class="eyebrow">Archive</p>
    <h2 id="posts-title">Latest posts</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="post-grid">
  {% for post in collections.posts %}
    <article class="post-card">
      <p class="post-card__date"><time datetime="{{ post.data.updated or post.data.date }}">{{ post.data.date | dateDisplay }}{% if post.data.updated %} · Updated {{ post.data.updated | dateDisplay }}{% endif %}</time></p>
      <h3><a href="{{ site.basePath }}{{ post.data.slug }}.html">{{ post.data.title | safe }}</a></h3>
      <p>{{ post.data.summary or post.data.description }}</p>
      {% if post.data.tags and post.data.tags.length %}
      <ul class="tag-list" aria-label="Tags">
        {% for tag in post.data.tags.slice(0, 5) %}<li>{{ tag }}</li>{% endfor %}
      </ul>
      {% endif %}
    </article>
  {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>

<footer class="page-footer" data-pagefind-ignore>
  <p><a href="https://github.com/anyech/jingxiao-cai-blog">GitHub Repository</a></p>
</footer>
